name: Gavyn_Sykes
content:
Gavyn Sykes is a human male who served in the Royal Naboo Security Forces as an N-1 starfighter pilot. He flew in Bravo Squadron during the Invasion of Naboo as Bravo Six. At the time, he had been assigned the astromech droid R2-C4.
Gavyn Sykes first appeared as a supporting artiste in the 1999 film Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace. In the current canon, he was first identified on the product page of an ARTFX + series R2-C4 figure released by the Japanese toy company KOTOBUKIYA CO., LTD. in December 2014. On that page, he is referred to as ギャヴィン・サイケス in Japanese katakana characters, and the English spelling is not specified.
